doctype html
html
    head
    img(src='http://webstoremall.com/images/company/80/C_Casa_logo.jpg')
    h1 Booking informations from Casablanca with booking ID: <b>#{booking._id}</b>
    body
        p Hello <b>#{guests[0].firstName}</b>, this is a confirmation mail for your booking at Casablanca hotel resort.
        p You are booked in at room <b>#{booking.room}</b>, on <b>#{booking.startDate}</b> to <b>#{booking.endDate}</b>.
        p We have set up an account in our system, so you will get a personal username and password so you can book a facility.
        p Your guests include

            each g, index in guests
                ul
                    li First name: #{g.firstName}
                    li Last name : #{g.lastName}
                    li Address   : #{g.address}
                    li Country   : #{g.country}
                    li Email     : #{g.email}
                    li Phone     : #{g.phone}
                    li Birth date: #{g.dateOfBirth}
                    li <b><u>Username</u></b>  : #{usernpw[index].username}
                    li <b><u>Password</u></b>  : #{usernpw[index].password}
        p We welcome you to the hotel, and are looking forward to see you.
            p Kind regards, Casablanca Hotel Resort